          <text><![CDATA[<p>This joint resolution nullifies the rule submitted by the Office of Natural Resources Revenue titled &quot;Consolidated Federal Oil &amp; Gas and Federal &amp; Indian Coal Valuation Reform.&quot;The rule published in the Federal Register on July 1, 2016, addresses royalties generated from oil, gas, and coal production.</p>]]></text>
